% Source inspiration: set bc cards in the official pin-cell and assembly examples.
% Intentional simplification: valid minimal structure plus one unsupported reserved card.
% Expected findings: SG014 INFO for set; preserve the raw card and continue.

surf outersurf sqc 0.0 0.0 0.65

cell fuelcell 0 fuel -outersurf
cell outsidecell 0 outside outersurf

mat fuel -10.0
92235.09c -0.04
92238.09c -0.84
8016.09c -0.12

set bc 2
